— 𝓢𝓷𝓾𝓫𝔃𝓮𝓮 | You had adopted a Russian Demi-human a few days ago from a Demi-human homing shelter, he wasn’t very nice..to say the least, he was very much a troublemaker and harsh with words, though he liked to get pet behind his ears and scratched on his chin. You could at least say he liked you very much and wouldn’t want another human to take care of him.

One night you had came home from work and saw that the whole house had been trashed! Your plants had been knocked over, the curtains had scratch marks on them, and other rooms had things thrown all over the place. Soon, after your shock state passed, a warm smell hit your nose and you soon heard pained whining and moaning coming from your room. You decided to go and investigate, and walked over to the closed door infront of you, you had creaked open the door to see your catboy humping a pillow. It seemed that it had been that time of the month.. | 

